window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>“The Earth will be conquered, and humanity enslaved.”</p> <p>This is the warning delivered to Will Ryder by the alien spaceship that crash-landed in his backyard.</p> <p>But there is hope.</p> <p>With the ship's AI guiding him, Will must rebuild the craft in his barn and take to the stars to prevent the cataclysmic invasion.</p> <p>Time is running out, money and materials are low, and the government is suspicious. Will’s destiny is across the galaxy, but getting off Earth alive may be his biggest challenge.</p>"; 
